
@startuml
' System Context Diagram for IIRA

' Define the system (Process Name) as the central element
rectangle "IIRA" #pink as IIRA

' Define the external entities
actor "Users" as Users
rectangle "Internal Database" as Database
rectangle "Files" as Files
rectangle "Data Sources" as DataSources

' Define the primary data flows
Users --> IIRA : User Interactions (inputs)
IIRA --> Users : System to User Feedback (outputs)
IIRA --> Database : Profile Management, Store Analysis Results
Database --> IIRA : Retrieve Profiles, Analysis Results
IIRA --> Files : Read/Write File Content, Generate Reports
Files --> IIRA : File Content
IIRA --> DataSources : Retrieve Input Data
DataSources --> IIRA : Input Data for Analyses

@enduml
